{"tid":890641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"喪父之痛　演員戴耀明為母親拒北漂","createTime":"2018-11-05T12:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T21:18:04.000Z","uid":166857,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"28b10933450bef4ae8cad09a5cf472b25c62ac9d","tid":890641,"uid":166857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181105/bkn-20181105190021878-1105_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181105%2Fbkn-20181105190021878-1105_00862_001.html&d=w5yGqUan81Y6HPaDGCH1Wf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d6a6dd21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181105/bkn-20181105190021878-1105_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n無綫綠葉戴耀明1990年入行，入行至今已演出超過150部劇集，產量甚多！雖然他做的大多都是小角色，不過近年他終於苦盡甘來，在內地網劇《御姐嬌妻》中擔任男主角，認真威水。<br />\n<br />\n對戴耀明而言，雖然北上發展較為吃香，不過他一直放不低80歲的母親。自從爸爸過身之後，作為獨生子的戴耀明就與母親相依為命，更肩負起照顧母親的責任。戴耀明表示，曾試過有次北上工作，當時他的前女友通知他母親屙血，令他嚇得急急趕回香港。而戴耀明亦知道母親是他的第一位，所以面對豐厚的酬勞，他都拒絕北漂。此外，當提起丈夫，戴耀明媽媽都忍不住落淚，場面感人。<br />\n<br />\n睇左段訪問，平時攪攪笑笑，比人訪問都幾真性情、又小又老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得出好孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4753ca1eef10bf07322a2f72f1a54116690e1431","tid":890641,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"佢結左婚未?有無拖拍?"},{"pid":"027667d84b6b58e37b4c9ccb4ace84b1469eb522","tid":890641,"uid":50216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"排長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deeb9a3bcb38fd0c5daa77fecdaf0fe56c0cfff","tid":890641,"uid":166857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4753ca1eef10bf07322a2f72f1a54116690e1431","tid":890641,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20